If I could pick any two Mythical Crew members to hang out with for a day, rack up a bar tab, and collaborate on drunken gourmet eats, it'd definitely be Emily and Josh. Thanks for giving me some insight into into what that day would be like.

For another episode, maybe show us the classic lightly spruced-up ramen options VS a gourmet (overly expensive) take while using the same noodle pack to serve as a control in the experiment.
